OL,3,C5-year-old boy seriously injured after
OL,4,Cbeing hit by car
OL,6,FA five-year-old boy has been injured
OL,7,Fafter being hit by a car in Scunthorpe.
OL,9,FPolice were called to the Elizabeth
OL,10,FStreet area shortly after 2pm on
OL,11,FSaturday 2 May.
OL,13,FThe child, who was playing in the
OL,14,Fstreet, had suffered what are thought
OL,15,Fto be serious injuries.
OL,17,FOfficers are asking anyone who was in
OL,18,Fthe area at the time and witnessed the
OL,19,Fincident, or who has dashcam footage
OL,20,Ffrom the area, to get in touch.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/2
