OL,3,C5-year-old boy seriously injured after
OL,4,Cbeing hit by car
OL,6,FThey are appealing for driver of an
OL,7,Fice cream van to come forward.
OL,9,F"We are particularly keen to hear from
OL,10,Fthe driver of an ice cream van that
OL,11,Fwas seen in the area at the time as we
OL,12,Fbelieve they may have witnessed
OL,13,Fsomething that could assist our
OL,14,Fenquiries."
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
